{
  "stem": "14897.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I'm just telling you that to show you that my life whereas it wasn't, of course, as good as it had been before, I don't remember being hungry.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember studying and still living a life of or more or less a young-- a young person, a-- a young teenager.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember that my girlfriends were still interested in music.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, in-- we were just getting then swing from United States.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember they had some records that we played.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we tried to learn how to dance and-- so it was still a semi-normal life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The buildings were sort of organized to try to help the people who were really unfortunate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were what you would call soup kitchens practically in every apartment house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And what we had, we did share with other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But there were still very big differences in the-- in the level of-- of quality of life of different people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was relatively little contact with the Germans, which is, of course, a big advantage of a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It has many disadvantages.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- but you didn't constantly encounter the Germans, so you-- you-- I was never beaten, for example.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Incidentally in the whole war, I was never beaten.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I've seen it, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But personally, just randomly, I was not beaten.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just luck.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just luck.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To have survived the war, you had to have luck many times and wits many times, you know, quick wits.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, of course, being a child, can only attribute the quick wits to my father primarily, which he did have, and to luck, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, God.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can not carry a tune.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Look, just pure statistics.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
